steps.name: From main page choose any product and add to cart
Navigate to the checkout page and fill in valid user information
Verify that url redirected to second part of checkout
Verify second part consist of payment and delivery information
Once checkout information confirmed to be expected, finish the checkout
Click back home button and return to main page

labels.name: feature
labels.value: Successful Checkout with Valid User Information

labels.name: story
labels.value: Verify that a user with valid information can successfully complete the checkout process and reach the order confirmation page.
